The paper proposes physical layer security techniques for millimeter wave vehicular communication systems, which involves the transmission of information symbols and noise-like signals using multiple antennas. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Multimedia (cs.MM), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
